.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n煎牛扒其實最難控制就係火候同時間<br />\n<br />\n兩樣野其中一樣掌握唔好的話，就好容易整得太熟<br />\n<br />\n所以有Ｄ人就會首先用液體氮將塊牛扒整凍先<br />\n<br />\n然後先攞去煎，而且要好高溘，講緊係可能４００幾度<br />\n<br />\n咁就牛扒表面就會快速進行梅納反應，而入面就咁易熟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1697f166d0fb0a6127db3e29b1fa1e1d425e76","tid":106134,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"一陣毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0b293aa2a95130a0b6d27f0c16fa40bfb66726","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一陣毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有命你叫，生化毒男嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b12a5306331ed4e93585d21744ffb1d27233db","tid":106134,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"hi jack"},{"pid":"abad06c140d212ee4c1828b4e1533cbeda6707a5","tid":106134,"uid":66603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"香味主要原因唔係因為油咩?"},{"pid":"a063dcf670f6c431902afb0dceeff5f1e3be8878","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi jack</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi 大門大獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f44b93755537085e9e07abf5be00ee7f829f86","tid":106134,"uid":18388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b568c77133223da9abd28909f509f4084c9d3507","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香味主要原因唔係因為油咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咦，巴打好似都有Ｄ認識喎<br />\n<br />\n香味同油都有好密切既關係架<br />\n<br />\n例如油有ester呢個functional group，係其中一個導致香味既重要化合物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，其實仲有其他類型既化合物都會有香味既<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aroma_compound#Cyclic-terpenes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAroma_compound%23Cyclic-terpenes&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhptibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a29ddde2\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aroma_compound#Cyclic-terpenes</a><br />\n<br />\n講到底，所謂既香味只係一堆化合物<br />\n<br />\n而梅納反應就係其中一個產生呢Ｄ化合物既反應，其他既有我係片入面既焦糖化反應 （caramelization）　等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85650f4bfc4e57fb52d72c62ed138d1d022e181","tid":106134,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:42:52.000Z","msg":"咁都有得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5931c8fc143ca70b5892225120cd30fae06ef16","tid":106134,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:48:17.000Z","msg":"但條片都唔錯既，輕輕一推"},{"pid":"1ab5c2f9420b085bfe33d3a98d20593a1f477220","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但條片都唔錯既，輕輕一推</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb5be024e5afb0952e4b12133981c245ba81323","tid":106134,"uid":1201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但條片都唔錯既，輕輕一推</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\