/blockquote><br />\n所以煎牛扒落一大舊牛油就會好好味<br />\n當然唔係浸住啦<br />\n要係咁淋上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係咁"},{"pid":"26e407c288ba34ca5b9548d58bbe07a296b3d96b","tid":106134,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"755ee2da69f9a90e88793999013c6562fe80bcf1","tid":106134,"uid":10793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個係我地既Facebook Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jackszetoch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjackszetoch&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhptibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=840bed83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jackszetoch</a><br />\n<br />\n可以入黎逛下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個你個人fb黎咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bc61fa87cf02ea29e06b9682e83abf756e8066","tid":106134,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"放過樓主啦，條片都幾好睇吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHi jack <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01343203cdab2966263b5803aed1342088a58dc","tid":106134,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"6af58bd691b197330e6232480a3d4a8385088de6","tid":106134,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"幾有趣"},{"pid":"9a75f44270636f4eb4d7fc1367ebf8cacafe78fd","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香味主要原因唔係因為油咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咦，巴打好似都有Ｄ認識喎<br />\n<br />\n香味同油都有好密切既關係架<br />\n<br />\n例如油有ester呢個functional group，係其中一個導致香味既重要化合物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，其實仲有其他類型既化合物都會有香味既<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aroma_compound#Cyclic-terpenes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAroma_compound%23Cyclic-terpenes&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhptibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a29ddde2\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aroma_compound#Cyclic-terpenes</a><br />\n<br />\n講到底，所謂既香味只係一堆化合物<br />\n<br />\n而梅納反應就係其中一個產生呢Ｄ化合物既反應，其他既有我係片入面既焦糖化反應 （caramelization）　等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以煎牛扒落一大舊牛油就會好好味<br />\n當然唔係浸住啦<br />\n要係咁淋上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實雖然原理簡單，但細節就好複雜既<br />\n唔同食物會有唔同化合物產生，仲係一次產生過百種<br />\n所以到呢家都有仲有人研究緊梅納反應架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936198a975455bb9ca119782469b035dbe003cb3","tid":106134,"uid":18319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:09:39.000Z","msg":"屌樓主高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c2152744eb5bcecc42b6d198f626a00a706810","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌樓主高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家FOCUS係段片度，唔好FOCUS係我度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e64fdc9158cf3cd1a0d25a0ceec889a79cabc88","tid":106134,"uid":59943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教下shaw can 啲廚點用化學知識煮好啲？"},{"pid":"073a8b7d89f1f6fd7817726c2063c2dd31b03a79","tid":106134,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"咁都有得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63f484e4cc17b34800369baf99a0ddd8f2a0e9f","tid":106134,"uid":71847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"bb508d0cffd3c8f54120611b1a6fd0f078c55e73","tid":106134,"uid":47426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d609665342e7253390747a4ac288da9ef068b87b","tid":106134,"uid":81747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以教下shaw can 啲廚點用化學知識煮好啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nShaw can 是屎<br />\n冇得救<br />\n用TNT炸左佢係最好既解決方法<br />\n<br />\n利申: 當年都間唔中要食shaw can<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f6d4924a50503386ebaa37260c5e0ad916cb70","tid":106134,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1323b60b852b4d1935a52ce97de171d723eedbad","tid":106134,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"高質，已sub<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce4214f8e938f09